<div id="article" class="article-new">
	<h1>Passion of the crust: How to make the perfect pie</h1>
	</em>
</p>
<p class="tagline">Sales of pies are soaring, there are  more varieties on offer than ever &ndash; and they even have their own awards ceremony.</p>
	<p class="author">
            <author>
					By Simon Usborne</author><br/>
            </p>

		<div class="clear-o">
			<p class="info"><em>Thursday, 18 February 2010</em></p>

			<ul class="article-tools">
